data.enText: a long tube in the body between the stomach and the anus . Food passes from the stomach to the small intestine and from there to the large intestine .

tr: the part of the alimentary canal between the stomach and the anus

value.def: Your intestines are the tubes in your body through which food passes when it has left your stomach.

example.ex: This area is always tender to the touch if the intestines are not functioning properly...
example.tran: 如果肠功能不正常,这个部位碰一下就会感到疼痛。

example.ex: This vitamin is absorbed through the walls of the small intestine.
example.tran: 这种维生素通过小肠壁被吸收。
